SetStartNetworkFeature

virtual FDO_API void FdoINetworkShortestPathCommand::SetStartNetworkFeature (  GisString *  className,
FdoPropertyValueCollection *  featId
)  [pure virtual]
 

This method is used to set the starting point of the network analysis. The starting network feature must be set before the command is executed.

Parameters:
className is the class name of the start feature. This is used in combination with the feat id to find the feature instance where the analysis should start.
featId is a collection of the identity property values.
Returns:
Returns nothing
